body:
## Announcements

R4 conference is 19/10/2016. Great chance to try your hand at a competition. for more information please visit http://r4.msuaitp.com/

ACM programming contest is 05/11/2016 from 12:30 until 17:30. Lunch, dinner, and a T-Shirt will be provided. The contest is organized in teams of 3 students each, please contact Robin Powell to say you are interested.

## Next Meeting 02/11/2016

Our department head and fearless leader, Dr. Ken Vollmar, will be presenting. We will be giving away the prize money from the competition. We will also have pizza. Be sure to watch for the email for more information.
